                    <span>My wife and I have found Gerry's book to be invaluable in getting the beta necessary to climb Colorado's 14ers. His consistent no-nonsense approach gives climbers what they need for a successful experience. We keep the book on the coffee table year-round and often thumb through it in the dead of winter, looking forward to our next adventure.</span>
                  
